{"tid":1861340,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"從馬基雅維利嘅君王論去解釋港共點解唔全面封關","createTime":"2020-02-04T05:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T06:36:51.000Z","uid":270506,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"883c6aff68e1c9f10aeaf8738095954e5a585ded","tid":1861340,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"君王論<br />\n（引自<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikisource.org/zh-hant/君主論）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%E5%90%9B%E4%B8%BB%E8%AB%96%EF%BC%89&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=9f04b5a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikisource.org/zh-hant/君主論）</a><br />\n//第05章、對於佔領前在各自的法律下生活的城市或君主國應當怎樣統治<br />\n<br />\n如果<strong>被征服的國家</strong>，象上面所說的那樣，向來<strong>習慣於在它們自己的法律之下自由 地生活</strong>的話，那麼想要保有這種國家有三種辦法：<br />\n<br />\n其一是，把它們毀滅掉；<br />\n其二是，親自前往駐在那裡（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警+人口換血</span></strong>）；<br />\n其三是，允許它們在它們自己的法律之下生活，同時要它們進貢並且在那個國家裡面建立一個對你友好的寡頭政府（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港共偽政權</span></strong>）<br />\n<br />\n因為這樣的一個政府是由君主建立的，它知道如果不倚靠他的友誼和力量，它就不能夠繼續存在，於是竭其全力擁護君主。而且如果君主想要保有一個向來習慣於自由 生活的城市，那麼藉助於這個城市的市民比依靠任何其他方法容易得多。<br />\n<br />\n斯巴達人和羅馬人就是兩個例子①。斯巴達人依靠在當地建立一個寡頭政府來控制雅典和底比斯；但是結果仍然失掉雅典和底比斯。羅馬人為着保有卡普阿②、迦太基③和努曼齊阿④，把它們毀滅了，就沒有失去它們。可是羅馬人想同斯巴達人那樣保有希臘，讓它享有自由 並且允許它的法律存在，他們卻沒有獲得成功。因此，<strong>他們為着保有希臘，不得不把那個地區的許多城市加以破壞。因為要穩固地佔有它們，除了毀滅它們之外，確實沒有別的辦法</strong>。從而任何人一旦成為一個城市的主子，如果這個城市原來習慣於自由 的生活，而他不把這個城市消滅，他就是坐待它把自己消滅。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為這個城市在叛亂的時候，總是利用自由 的名義和它的古老的秩序作為藉口</span></strong>。而這兩者儘管經過悠久的歲月或者施恩授惠都不能夠使人們忘懷。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">除非將那裡的居民弄得四分五裂或者東離西散，否則無論你怎麼辦或者怎樣預防，他們還是永遠不會忘掉那個名義和那種秩序的</span></strong>，正如在佛羅倫薩人羈絆下百年後的皮薩一樣，人們遇有任何不測之事就立即想起它們。//<br />\n<br />\n以下係基於上面呢段引文而得嘅要點：<br />\n1. 中共用第二同第三個方法都唔能夠止暴制亂征服香港嘅時候，好大機會轉用第一個方法，毀滅200萬為數不少異己，可以點做？<br />\n老解入城?-&gt;香港冇咗獨立關稅區地位，支那融唔到資-&gt;支爆。<br />\n用唔到老解，用<strong>肺炎</strong>?-&gt;香港冇咗啲人口，跟住加速換血，令新香港對其徹底忠誠，又可以繼續融資<br />\n<br />\n今次港共遲遲都唔全面封關，再加上今日中旅（中共）加密深圳灣班次加速播毒，可見呢次極有可能係中共嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">生化戰</span></strong>！大家要做好本地+國際文宣，指控共匪企圖用武漢肺炎嘅疫情嚟謀害香港人！<br />\n<br />\n另外，除咗罷工之外，唔好唔記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國戰線</span></span></strong>，向美國遊說請求美國就封關事宜以及85000僑民嘅性命安全向港共施壓，同埋邀請CDC派員嚟香港協助抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fexert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=5ebea391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=934866b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-cdcs-support-battle-against-2019-ncov-outbreak-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter：<br />\nNCM Yue<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=f4c8971c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue</a><br />\n美國國務院<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StateDept\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStateDept&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=f07ebbff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StateDept</a><br />\n美國駐港總領事館<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAinHKMacau&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=f4ed2603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau</a><br />\n<br />\nFb：<br />\n美國駐港總領事館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USAinHKMacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSAinHKMacau&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e82a7bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/USAinHKMacau</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 自由價值+傳統係對抗侵略者嘅利器<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切勿分化</span></strong>！分化無容置疑係對侵略者有利，反共陣營即使有咩分歧，都唔好互割，面對強敵點都要聯合起嚟"},{"pid":"b2a7754780c9c5b04ab3639631be0301b7523e86","tid":1861340,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfcefa640636884ceff2b9fe14c421a1e9d4229","tid":1861340,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"大家請幫手推，p牌仔推唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf60139c92b40d3479d4ba4703d67aa518d245d","tid":1861340,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"754c14993e2f6fc7d71ea3e6d2b72ccc47cd8f25","tid":1861340,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"4c9e09e1f551492c6ec6847e701547d311a50b42","tid":1861340,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"1e09866d74737cf32079ca90ef24e89f7459559a","tid":1861340,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:56:01.000Z","msg":"4/10 天滅中共"},{"pid":"443